> problem.

There is a structure in the NewTypes called "MenuItem" for each item on the
menu.

This has a Flags parameter which can be either:

#NM_MENUDISABLED  or  #NM_MENUENABLED for NewLook Menus

or for standard menus it will be:

#MENUENABLED or #MENUDISABLED


I never tried doing anything with these, but I think this is the place to
start.

Later...
